  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the tandoor to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Soak 12 bamboo skewers in water for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Thread 1-2 pieces of each vegetable and black pudding onto each skewer.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together minced garlic and olive oil.",
    "Brush the garlic oil onto the skewers, then season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Place the skewers in the preheated tandoor and cook for 8-10 minutes, or until the black pudding is crispy and golden brown.",
    "Brush the skewers with honey (if using) and serve hot."
